riften und in der Werbung jener Zeit. Darüber hinaus erlaubtsie neue Erkenntnisse zu den Themen und Mechanismen der faschistischen Propaganda.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Mrz 2018) 0aFascist propagandazItaly. 0aPhotomontagezItalyxHistoryy20th century.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2015z9783110438642oZDB-23-DKA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG0 cEPUBz978-3-11-038073-60 cprintz978305006098940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783050094953423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783050094953.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DKAb2015